Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:10.03,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}多餘的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:13.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就讓我先睡一覺再說
